BBCalc - BodyBuilding Calculators
=================================

Description:

	BBCalc (BodyBuilding Calculators) is a set of calculators related 
	to bodybuilding and fitness topics.

Dependencies:

	* Python 2.4 and above
	* wxPython 2.8 and above
	
	Application was tested to work in Ubuntu Dapper and Windows 2000.
	
	Note: Please, give me a note if it's working in other environment
	and with dependencies versions other than above.

Installation:

	TODO: Write installation instruction
	
	Just unzip and than execute command 'make install' in BBCalc directory.
	
